commit.message: Change default suggested install method, add settings compilation instructions, don't assume X11
Updated changelog and bumped version for release (v40.0)
Remove unused patching function
Use '===' for folder order checking
Update extension's description
Use Controls to get access to appDisplay instance
Remove extra newline
Share AppSystem with extension
Drop unused inport from AppGridHelper
Drop extra instance of folder settings
Avoid running Shell.AppSystem.get_default() more than necessary
Patch AppDisplay prototype instead of the running instance
Only send patch debug messages when the functions are actually patched by the shell
Stop using AppDisplay as a global between 2 files
Drop extra _redisplay() call
Remove unnecessary alphabeticalSortName() function
Fix folder previews and contents getting stuck
Update changelog and bump version for release (v39.0)
Add GNOME 46 support to metadata
Updated changelog and bumped version for release (v38.0)
Move AppSystem inside constructor
Update changelog and bump version for release (v37.0)
Fix inconsistent styling
Fix constructor calling non-existent functions
Rename _logMessage to _debugMessage
Don't call get_default() every time the app system is used
Restructure AppGridManager to manage itself
Merge listener connection into one function
Use connectObject and disconnectObject
